name: thrift
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.10.0" %}
{% set hash_type = "sha256" %}
{% set hash = "b7f6c09155321169af03f9fb20dc15a4a0c7481e7c334a5ba8f7f0d864633209" %}
{% set name = "thrift" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.zip
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.zip
  {{ hash_type }}: {{ hash }}

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - six >=1.7.2

  run:
    - python
    - six >=1.7.2

test:
  imports:
    - thrift
    - thrift.protocol
    - thrift.server
    - thrift.transport

about:
  home: http://thrift.apache.org
  license: Apache 2.0
  summary: 'Python bindings for the Apache Thrift RPC system'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mariusvniekerk
    - ericdill
    - marshall245

about.summary: Python bindings for the Apache Thrift RPC system
